Phase 1 Architecture

Purpose

Phase 1 establishes the foundation of the SentinelOps platform.

The objective is to create a minimal production-style microservices environment consisting of:

* Event Ingestion Service
* Alert Service
* PostgreSQL Database
* Docker Compose Deployment

This phase focuses on validating the core architecture, service communication patterns, database connectivity, and development workflow before introducing additional services and operational capabilities in later phases.
